29:32.406 --> 29:33.322
It's starting.

29:33.324 --> 29:35.524
(Chanting continues)

29:51.019 --> 29:53.520
(Women chanting)

29:55.221 --> 29:56.322
Aya.

29:56.324 --> 29:57.657
We may have an issue.

29:57.659 --> 30:00.360
(Chanting continues)

30:04.115 --> 30:05.532
I need you to focus.

30:05.534 --> 30:06.783
Show me what represents you,

30:06.785 --> 30:08.251
