30:08.253 --> 30:10.370
- The kings.
- (Grunts)

30:10.372 --> 30:12.455
The knights.

30:15.064 --> 30:16.209
If you've lost contact,

30:16.211 --> 30:18.962
send men to the front
gate to check the...

30:26.013 --> 30:28.221
(Shouting, screaming)

30:33.551 --> 30:35.691
Well, if it isn't Rayna Cruz!

30:36.898 --> 30:39.566
(Grunting, clamoring)

30:43.166 --> 30:44.037
Which is it?

30:44.039 --> 30:45.538
The kings or the knights?

30:45.540 --> 30:47.240
We need to decide now.

30:47.242 --> 30:50.643
(Women chanting)

30:56.251 --> 30:57.022
(Grunts)

30:57.052 --> 30:59.102
- Marcel!
- I'm sorry, D.

30:59.426 --> 31:01.855
We need to get them
out of that water now.

31:01.857 --> 31:03.292
No!

31:03.322 --> 31:04.538
(Shouts)

31:05.644 --> 31:07.026
How perfect.

31:07.028 --> 31:09.819
Even in this crucial
hour, your ignorance

31:09.849 --> 31:11.270
