31:11.498 --> 31:14.595
Even if you never learn from your sins,

31:14.911 --> 31:16.443
at least you will die

31:16.473 --> 31:19.572
because of them and I get to watch.

31:20.792 --> 31:21.792
(Panting)

31:23.122 --> 31:24.711
Take the queens.

31:24.713 --> 31:26.045
The women we betrayed

31:26.047 --> 31:27.547
represent us.

