so much left to say.

35:58.533 --> 36:00.866
(Crying)

36:00.868 --> 36:02.418
I can't lose you again, Tristan.

36:02.420 --> 36:04.086
I won't lose you again.

36:04.088 --> 36:05.755
I'm sorry.

36:05.757 --> 36:07.373
(Rumbling continues)

36:07.375 --> 36:08.841
I love you.

36:09.553 --> 36:10.509
No.

36:10.511 --> 36:12.011
(Coughing)

36:13.047 --> 36:16.048
No. No.

36:17.552 --> 36:19.885
(Aurora crying)

36:19.887 --> 36:21.392
(Aurora screams)

36:21.422 --> 36:22.755
No!

36:23.768 --> 36:25.341
(Sobbing)

36:30.014 --> 36:32.181
Welcome back to the real world, luv.

36:32.712 --> 36:34.400
I thought we might revisit our chat

36:34.402 --> 36:36.402
about what hurts and what does not.

36:36.404 --> 36:37.520
(Sobs)

36:37.522 --> 36:39.155
(Grunts)

36:43.003 --> 36:44.777
Courtesy of my dear sister.

36:44.779 --> 36:47.268
Oh... what are you doing?

36:47.298 --> 36:48.914
You made me realize today

36:48.916 --> 36:50.883
what a monster I've been,

36:50.885 --> 36:55.921
and I am sorry that I
didn't do this sooner.

36:58.593 --> 37:00.309
You can't just leave me here!

37:02.263 --> 37:05.848
I had the right idea when
I bricked up your portrait.

37:05.850 --> 37:08.150
Behind walls is where you belong.

37:08.534 --> 37:09.935
Then just kill me.

37:09.937 --> 37:11.682
Please, Nik, just kill me!

37:11.712 --> 37:13.689
Oh, I think not.

37:13.691 --> 37:15.658
Not with the only one who loves you

37:15.660 --> 37:17.943
rotting at the bottom of the ocean.

37:18.476 --> 37:20.446
I wouldn't grant you the mercy.

37:20.448 --> 37:21.747
So, while the fish eat him...

37:21.749 --> 37:22.915
No.

37:22.917 --> 37:24.917
And the worms eat you,

37:24.919 --> 37:30.256
just know it was I who
took everything from you.

37:30.258 --> 37:31.674
(Sobs)

37:39.104 --> 37:41.517
- Here.
- Where's my stuff?

37:41.519 --> 37:42.968
Your bag's over there.

37:44.195 --> 37:46.572
I figured, after what you
did, I'd better get you out

37:46.574 --> 37:48.346
before the Mikaelsons
came back to hurt you.

37:49.001 --> 37:50.293
You mean like you hurt me?

37:50.295 --> 37:53.212
I asked you to do one thing for me.

37:53.614 --> 37:55.147
To believe in me.

37:55.149 --> 37:57.283
To choose my side.

37:57.285 --> 38:00.069
I asked you to choose me.

38:00.741 --> 38:02.215
But you didn't.

38:02.882 --> 38:03.759
Wait, D.

38:03.789 --> 38:05.408
Listen. Hey.

38:06.341 --> 38:07.593
Listen.

38:07.595 --> 38:08.978
I am always on your side.

38:08.980 --> 38:11.314
All right? I always have your back.

38:11.316 --> 38:13.816
But sometimes the things that you want,

38:13.818 --> 38:16.185
