you have to pay to get them.

38:16.729 --> 38:17.937
Yeah?

38:18.451 --> 38:19.772
Keep telling yourself that.

38:22.233 --> 38:23.526
Enjoy your freedom.

38:31.675 --> 38:34.120
So... the spell worked.

38:34.503 --> 38:35.621
We survived.

38:35.623 --> 38:38.674
I saved you and you saved me.

38:39.540 --> 38:41.177
Funny how that works, isn't it?

38:41.179 --> 38:42.795
Mm.

38:42.797 --> 38:45.381
I'd be happy to let this be the end.

38:45.683 --> 38:46.982
Am I too optimistic in thinking

38:46.984 --> 38:48.317
