38:48.319 --> 38:49.602
Well, that depends.

38:49.604 --> 38:51.353
Are you going to do the right thing?

38:51.355 --> 38:54.490
By whom? I assume you
don't mean my brother.

38:55.059 --> 38:57.276
By her.

39:01.833 --> 39:02.825
(Sighs)

39:02.855 --> 39:04.917
I love her.

39:04.919 --> 39:08.420
I know that you did once, too.

39:08.422 --> 39:11.290
I promise I will only do right by her.

39:15.146 --> 39:16.646
Thank you.

39:24.605 --> 39:25.988
