39:34.876 --> 39:36.916
For some reason, she cares about you.

39:38.024 --> 39:40.252
Enough to risk her own life.

39:40.616 --> 39:42.171
Take your own advice.

39:42.462 --> 39:43.839
Do right by her.

39:48.463 --> 39:50.012
